<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MEMBERS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/team.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>MEMBERS OF CLUB</h1>
    <p><b>There are mutltiple roles in a club and each role is equally important for success of club</b></p>
    <div>
        <div class="section-container left">
            <div class="sec">
                <p>
                    <h3>SECRETARYS</h3>
                    Secratarys are main administrative head of the club.<br>
                    They manage official documentation, communication, and oversee overall club operations.<br>
                    They ensure meetings, events, and club activities run smoothly.<br>
                    There are  5 secratarys of our club
                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/home/team/sec';">Secratary Details...</button>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="section-container right">
            <div class="mentor">
                <p>
                    <h3>MENTORS</h3>
                        Mentors are experienced members who guide and support junior members.<br>
                        They provide advice, training, and help in skill development related to club activities.<br>
                        There are 2 mentors in our club

                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/home/team/mentor';">Mentor Details...</button>
       
            </div>
        </div>




        <div class="section-container left">
            <div class="jec">
                <p>
                    <h3>JOINT SECRETARYS</h3>
                    Joint secratary assists the Secretary in administrative tasks.<br>
                    They help in coordinating club activities and step in when the Secretary is unavailable.<br>
                    There are 4 jsec of our club
                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/home/team/jsec';">JSec Details...</button>
        
            </div>
        </div>




    <div class="section-container right">

        <div class="ih">
            <p>
                <h3>INNOVATIVE HEADS</h3>
                Innovative heads are responsible for bringing new ideas, creative solutions, and unique
                event concepts to keep the club dynamic and engaging.<br>
                They focus on brainstorming and implementing innovations.<br>
                Since there are teams we have multiple heads for them

            </p>
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/home/team/ih';">Heads Details...</button>
        
        </div>
    </div>



    <div class="section-container left">


        <div class="sc">
        <p>
            <h3>SENIOR COORDINATOR</h3>
            Senior coordinator manages specific teams or events, ensuring smooth execution.<br>
            They delegate tasks, maintain team coordination, and assist in the overall functioning of the club.<br>
        </p>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/home/team/sc';">Coordinators Details...</button>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

    <script>

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.section-container');
            
            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
                entries.forEach(entry => {
                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                        entry.target.classList.add('visible');
                    }
                });
            }, {
                threshold: 0.1
            });
            
            sections.forEach(section => {
                observer.observe(section);
            });
        });
    </script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.0.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>




